data.description: Welcome to 105 Masserta Court, a delightful residence in Las Vegas, showcasing freshly painted walls and cabinets for a modern touch. This 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home features a convenient 1-car garage. This home comes equipped with owned and paid-off solar panels. Located just minutes from the 15 Starr Exit, accessibility is a breeze, and the nearby St Rose Parkway offers an abundance of shopping and dining options, enhancing the convenience and lifestyle appeal of this location. Step inside to discover an inviting living area that seamlessly connects to a dining space, perfect for gatherings. The kitchen boasts a blend of modernity and functionality, with newly painted cabinets adding to the joy of meal preparation. Each bedroom is spacious and filled with natural light, offering a cozy retreat.
